SIMPLE: weekly
RECORDS: 3

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Weekly
<hw>Week"ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Of or
pertaining to a week, or week days; <as>as, <ex>weekly</ex>
labor</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Coming, happening, or done once a week; hebdomadary;
<as>as, a <ex>weekly</ex> payment; a <ex>weekly</ex>
gazette.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Weekly</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Weekly
<hw>Week"ly</hw>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Weeklies</plw>
<pr>(<?/)</pr>.</plu> <def>A publication issued once in seven days, or
appearing once a week.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Weekly</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Weekly
<hw>Week"ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Once a week; by hebdomadal
periods; <as>as, each performs service <ex>weekly</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Weekwam</ent>⟦br⟧
